dc_title_s: Lake Shore Features, Derived from the GNIS: Indiana
dc_description_s: Lake_features_usgs_in is a point shapefile showing the locations and attribute values of lake features extracted from the Geographic Names Information System (GNIS) developed by the USGS. Features include the following: bay, bar beach, cape, harbor, island.  The dataset contains lake features named on USGS 1:24000 quadrangles and other source map data.  Consider using this file along with files for stream features, natural features, and swamp points.
